org.nd4j.linalg.dataset.api

Interface MultiDataSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiDataSet

    public interface MultiDataSet
extends java.io.Serializable
    MultiDataSet is an interface for representing complex data sets, that have (potentially) multiple inputs and outputs For example, some complex neural network architectures may have multiple independent inputs, and multiple independent outputs. These inputs and outputs need not even be the same type of data: for example, images in and sequences out, etc
